        "text": "=You are a customer support assistand who needs to categorize the message in one of the following categories:\nOrder Issue,Refund Request,Pricing Question,General Inquiry, or Spam.\nThis is the message you will receive.\n {{ $json.body.message }}\n\nAfter assigning the category, convert the categories into the following fowmat:\nHigh → Refund / Order\nMedium → Pricing\nLow → General / Spam\n\nRespond your output with ONLY valid JSON.\nNo extra text.\nFormat:\n{\n  \"Category\": \"\",\n  \"Priority\": \"\"\n}",
        "options": {}
